snippet.title: Jurassic World Evolution 2: Dominion Malta Expansion | Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Jurassic World Evolution 2: Dominion Malta Expansion is Out Now on Steam, Epic Games Store, PlayStation Store, Xbox Store, Windows Store and Nvidia GeForce Now.

Out Now: https://www.jurassicworldevolution2.com/news/dominion-malta-expansion-and-free-update-5-out-now

Before the events of Jurassic World Dominion, help lead a brand-new enterprise in Malta. Work alongside Cabot Finch and key figures from the film, including Kayla Watts (voiced by DeWanda Wise), Soyona Santos (voiced by Dichen Lachman), Barry Sembène (voiced by Omar Sy), and Lewis Dodgson (voiced by Campbell Scott) as you set up parks across three Mediterranean locations. With the Authorities and the Underground both taking a keen interest in your operation across the area, who you choose to align with will unlock more opportunities to develop your parks. The expansion also contains a range of gameplay features, including the cargo ship and dinosaur exchange to challenge you further, as well as stunning new species, variants and skin.

For more news and information about Jurassic World Evolution 2:

Website: www.jurassicworldevolution2.com 
Facebook: facebook.com/JurassicWorldEvolution 
Twitter: www.twitter.com/JW_Evolution 
Instagram: @jurassicworldevolution
